name: AIGA Graphic Design
details: The American Institute for Graphic Arts chapter in Blacksburg includes designers from around the Blacksburg, Radford, and Roanoke area.

name: Blacksburg Cinema of Code
details: This is a group for software developers of any skill level, in any language. We'll meet to watch a training video, then discuss it afterwards. Inspired by CleanCoders offer of a Community License for free meetings that are open to the public, so I hope that some of their videos will be the first we review. I'll post a meeting once I have the license secured, so go ahead and join the group if you're interested so you'll receive the notifications.
